ted":false},{"text":"Prepare sales teams for adherence to lead conversion process; provide training during upcoming GPS training sessions (17:57)","completed":false},{"text":"Coordinate with Maria for campaign alignment and system communication improvements (19:24)","completed":false},{"text":"Review masking and field mapping recommendations as needed (35:00)","completed":false},{"text":"Assist Christina with calendar invite troubleshooting (07:17)","completed":false},{"text":"Assist Colin with project plan updates and coordination (00:00)","completed":false}]'::jsonb,
