WITH new_meeting AS (
  INSERT INTO compass_meetings (contract_id, meeting_date, source, external_id, title, participants, duration_seconds, recording_url, transcript, sentiment, raw_metadata, created_at, updated_at)
  VALUES (
    'cec48bff-a24c-43d2-a56e-4da7b806daf9',
    '2026-01-14 21:00:00+00',
    'fireflies',
    '01KED9N14A05VWDYJMW3NWNTWP',
    'EASE // MiD - Weekly Meeting',
    '{"Josh Santo","Paula Ocampo"}'::text[],
    365,
    'https://us04web.zoom.us/j/79575488295?pwd=XICgOPQC72fNribEyiumBtwmCmim8i.1',
    '{"id":"01KED9N14A05VWDYJMW3NWNTWP","title":"EASE // MiD - Weekly Meeting","summary":{"notes":"## **Content Production and Podcast Strategy**\n\nThe team is advancing content projects with a focus on delivering final assets and tracking audience engagement.\n\n- **The 2025 recap blog post is nearly complete, with copy set to be shared for review tomorrow with Cindy and Josh** to finalize the title and text (01:20)  \n    - This content aims to wrap up the year’s highlights, helping boost site traffic and brand authority.  \n    - Paula plans to gather feedback quickly to keep the timeline tight.  \n    - The blog’s completion supports broader content marketing goals for early 2025.  \n    - Timely publication is critical to capture interest while the year-end is still fresh.\n\n- **The podcast team is integrating animations into episodes, targeting inclusion in the upcoming MiD Weekly show** after the advice section (03:33)  \n    - This multimedia enhancement is intended to increase listener engagement and differentiate the podcast.  \n    - Josh emphasized the importance of tracking growth in listeners across Buzzsprout, YouTube, and Spotify.  \n    - Paula will coordinate with Bailey to identify the best way to monitor new reviews and listener feedback across platforms.  \n    - Having a clear review tracking process will help guide future content improvements and marketing efforts.\n\n## **Outreach Campaign Performance**\n\nThe outreach campaign launched and is showing early engagement signals that require monitoring for impact assessment.\n\n- **The email outreach campaign launched this morning and has already achieved between 10% to 30% email sends** through Smart Lead software (01:45)  \n    - Paula is actively monitoring incoming responses to measure campaign effectiveness and adjust tactics if needed.  \n    - Early send rates indicate the campaign is functioning as planned, supporting lead generation goals.  \n    - Continuous monitoring will provide insights to optimize messaging and targeting to improve conversion rates.  \n    - The campaign’s timely launch aligns with Q1 sales and marketing priorities to build momentum.\n\n## **Video Production and Delivery Timelines**\n\nVideo development is progressing with a clear deadline pressure to deliver training content by the end of January.\n\n- **The OTG training video’s first rough cut is expected early next week, with animations progressing well** (02:10)  \n    - Josh highlighted significant internal demand to complete all videos by January 31 for wider organizational use.  \n    - Paula committed to prioritizing animation work and adjusting team focus to meet the tight deadline.  \n    - Minimal post-production edits are hoped for, based on thorough preparatory work, to avoid delays.  \n    - Delivering on time will support training schedules and reduce pressure from stakeholders awaiting the content.\n\n## **Metrics Tracking and Review Process Improvements**\n\nThe team is setting up better ways to track podcast audience growth and reviews to inform content strategy.\n\n- **Josh requested regular tracking of podcast listener growth and new reviews across key platforms like Buzzsprout, YouTube, and Apple Podcasts** to measure engagement trends (03:58)  \n    - Paula plans to pull listener stats weekly for joint review, enabling data-driven decisions on content adjustments.  \n    - She will collaborate with Bailey to find an efficient way to aggregate and respond to reviews, avoiding platform fragmentation.  \n    - Streamlined review tracking will improve responsiveness to audience feedback and help spot trends early.  \n    - This effort is part of a broader push toward more measurable content marketing outcomes.","outline":null,"keywords":["Podcast","Outreach Campaign","Video Animation","OTG Training","Listener Metrics","Review Tracking"],"overview":"- **2025 Recap Blog Post:** Nearing completion, aims to boost traffic and brand authority; final review tomorrow.  \n- **Podcast Integration:** Animations to enhance episodes; monitoring growth on Buzzsprout, YouTube, and Spotify is crucial.  \n- **Outreach Campaign Launch:** Achieved 10% to 30% email sends; early engagement monitored to optimize messaging and conversion rates.  \n- **OTG Training Video:** First rough cut expected next week; all videos needed by January 31 amidst high demand.  \n- **Metrics Tracking Setup:** Weekly listener stats and reviews will guide content strategy; aiming for better audience engagement insights.","action_items":"\n**Paula Ocampo**\nShare 2025 recap blog copy and title options with Cindy and Josh for review tomorrow (01:20)\nMonitor outreach campaign progress and incoming messages post-launch (02:10)\nLiaise with animation team to prioritize OTG and other video animations for early delivery by end of January (03:11)\nIncorporate animation segment into upcoming MiD Weekly podcast episode after advice section (03:48)\nPull and prepare podcast growth statistics from Buzzsprout, YouTube, and Spotify for review next week (04:31)\nCoordinate with Bailey and team to explore review tracking tools and processes for Buzzsprout/Apple Podcasts and update Josh (05:22)\n\n**Josh Santo**\nSent podcast review request to Paula for animation integration into episodes (03:25)\n"},"duration":6.079999923706055,"speakers":[{"id":0,"name":"Josh Santo"},{"id":1,"name":"Paula Ocampo"}],"sentences":[{"text":"This meeting is being recorded.","index":0,"end_time":4.32,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2.64,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Hey there.","index":1,"end_time":25.93,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":25.61,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"How are you?","index":2,"end_time":27.61,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":26.81,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"I''m all right.","index":3,"end_time":28.61,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":28.01,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"How are you doing?","index":4,"end_time":30.33,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":28.61,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Great.","index":5,"end_time":30.81,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":30.41,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"How''s your week going so far?","index":6,"end_time":32.65,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":30.97,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"Oh, it''s very busy.","index":7,"end_time":35.37,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":33.53,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"I can''t believe it''s already January 14th.","index":8,"end_time":41.85,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":39.37,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"I know.","index":9,"end_time":42.65,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":42.01,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"It''s going the same.","index":10,"end_time":45.85,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":43.77,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":11,"end_time":47.13,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":46.65,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"Great.","index":12,"end_time":48.97,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":48.57,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"So I don''t have too many updates for you today, but I''m going to share my screen and share what I have.","index":13,"end_time":54.97,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":49.69,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"Okay.","index":14,"end_time":68.01,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":67.61,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"So I have some content updates regarding the blog, also the confirmation of the outreach campaign and some updates for the videos.","index":15,"end_time":79.21,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":68.09,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"Okay, so.","index":16,"end_time":80.83,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":79.45,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"So starting with the podcast, since we don''t have any episode in progress, we''re working on the 2025 recap block, which is already in progress and almost ready.","index":17,"end_time":93.18,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":80.98,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"I''m going to share tomorrow the copy with Cindy and you so you can review the title options and the copy and provide any feedback.","index":18,"end_time":102.5,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":93.18,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"Okay.","index":19,"end_time":103.3,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":102.74,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"And then for the outreach campaign, the campaigns launched this morning, I already have some email sends through a smart lead, so I think already reached 30% or 10%.","index":20,"end_time":120.53,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":105.3,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"I don''t remember right now, but it''s running and I''ll be looking for any messages that come true from the campaigns.","index":21,"end_time":130.13,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":120.77,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"Okay.","index":22,"end_time":130.93,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":130.37,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"And last, the updates that I have for the video are that our team is working on animations.","index":23,"end_time":140.63,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":133.33,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"We''re making good progress for the OTG training video, and we''ll have the first route cut probably ready by early next week.","index":24,"end_time":148.87,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":140.71,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"So.","index":25,"end_time":150.23,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":149.83,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"Yeah, that''s.","index":26,"end_time":151.87,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":150.95,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"That''s all I have.","index":27,"end_time":152.71,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":151.87,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"Thank you so much for approving all the audios.","index":28,"end_time":155.19,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":152.71,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"I think we''re making progress and we''re getting there.","index":29,"end_time":158.39,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":155.59,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"So I don''t know if you have anything for me.","index":30,"end_time":161.27,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":158.39,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"Yeah, I''m getting a lot of pressure to get the videos done, so it''d be great if we could have them done by the end of January.","index":31,"end_time":172.58,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":162.23,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"I. I know your team''s building the first drafts.","index":32,"end_time":176.1,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":173.62,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"I know this depends on, like, how much editing is needed afterwards, and we did all the work up front, so hopefully there''s no.","index":33,"end_time":183.22,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":176.82,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Not much editing needed.","index":34,"end_time":185.22,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":183.78,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"But just letting you know that got a lot of people being like, we want those videos.","index":35,"end_time":191.13,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":185.46,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Okay.","index":36,"end_time":192.33,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":191.85,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"Yeah, I totally get it.","index":37,"end_time":195.41,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":193.29,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"So I''m gonna talk with my team to see if we can prioritize some of the other videos, the animations, and see if we can have them ready as soon as possible.","index":38,"end_time":203.69,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":195.41,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"Totally get it.","index":39,"end_time":205.13,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":204.01,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"Yeah, that''d be great.","index":40,"end_time":206.49,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":205.53,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"And then I sent over the podcast review request.","index":41,"end_time":212.09,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":207.29,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Oh, yeah, thank you for that.","index":42,"end_time":215.29,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":213.13,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"Yeah, we''re actually working on the animation to include it in the podcast.","index":43,"end_time":220.49,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":215.29,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"I have a question regarding that.","index":44,"end_time":222.41,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":220.73,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"Do you want to include that part in MiD Weekly?","index":45,"end_time":224.73,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":222.41,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"Like, probably after the advice section.","index":46,"end_time":227.53,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":224.81,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":47,"end_time":228.33,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":227.85,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Okay, nice.","index":48,"end_time":229.69,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":228.49,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"Perfect.","index":49,"end_time":230.25,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":229.77,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"I want to confirm so we can have that ready probably for the next episode.","index":50,"end_time":236.17,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":230.57,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"Great.","index":51,"end_time":236.97,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":236.57,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Include that.","index":52,"end_time":237.77,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":237.05,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"And then I would love if on these check ins because you know we''re asking for reviews and stuff.","index":53,"end_time":243.77,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":238.65,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"If we just start tracking like any sort of the growth metrics, both just looking at like if there''s any growth as far as listeners across buzzsprout and YouTube.","index":54,"end_time":259.41,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":243.77,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"But then if, if any reviews pop up.","index":55,"end_time":263.37,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":260.05,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"If there''s an easy way to track reviews.","index":56,"end_time":266.65,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":263.37,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"I don''t.","index":57,"end_time":267.17,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":266.65,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"I know.","index":58,"end_time":267.73,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":267.17,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"I think it, I think that might be like platform specific though.","index":59,"end_time":271.05,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":267.81,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Like yeah, we can have some stats from Buzzsprout and from YouTube and Spotify.","index":60,"end_time":278.29,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":271.05,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"So I can pull those for the next week all and we can review them together.","index":61,"end_time":283.09,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":278.61,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"Yeah, totally.","index":62,"end_time":283.97,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":283.09,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"Okay.","index":63,"end_time":284.81,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":284.37,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"And then as far as like if we start seeing reviews, is there an easy way to look at them or do you have to go to each platform?","index":64,"end_time":294.61,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":284.81,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"I need to take a look and see because I''m not sure how it works with Buzz Proud and all that.","index":65,"end_time":301.44,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":295.09,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"So I need to talk with Bailey and see what is the best way to review those and get responder or something.","index":66,"end_time":308.16,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":302.24,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"So yeah, I''ll keep you posted.","index":67,"end_time":310.88,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":308.32,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"I assume that''s going to be the Apple podcast app because that''s looking at buzzsprout.","index":68,"end_time":317.88,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":311.6,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"That''s most of the audio listens, so.","index":69,"end_time":321.52,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":317.88,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"That''s right.","index":70,"end_time":322.68,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":322.16,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"Probably just look at that as the one spot which would be podcast connect, I think.","index":71,"end_time":329.05,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":322.68,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Anyway, yeah, I''ll take a look with, with the team and I''ll let you know.","index":72,"end_time":335.61,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":330.25,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"Or next week.","index":73,"end_time":337.77,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":335.85,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"Okay, sounds good.","index":74,"end_time":340.33,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":338.25,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Sounds good.","index":75,"end_time":341.29,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":340.65,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"So thank you for the time, Josh.","index":76,"end_time":342.89,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":341.29,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"You too.","index":77,"end_time":343.93,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":343.45,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Thank you.","index":78,"end_time":344.41,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":343.93,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Have a great day.","index":79,"end_time":345.73,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":344.81,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"Bye.","index":80,"end_time":346.17,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":345.73,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"Bye.","index":81,"end_time":349.93,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":346.33,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"}],"dateString":"2026-01-14T21:00:00.000Z","host_email":"paula.ocampo@marketersindemand.com","meeting_link":"https://us04web.zoom.us/j/79575488295?pwd=XIC