-- Meeting: Techmode+New North (2026-01-13 20:00:00+00)
WITH new_meeting AS (
  INSERT INTO compass_meetings (contract_id, meeting_date, source, external_id, title, participants, duration_seconds, recording_url, transcript, sentiment, raw_metadata, created_at, updated_at)
  VALUES (
    'b1f3ae44-0316-492e-aef1-bb260b814482',
    '2026-01-13 20:00:00+00',
    'fireflies',
    '01KEDG6KENV9NNCD9C6F4PHPZ6',
    'Techmode+New North',
    '{"Matthew Look","Colin Costigan","Christopher Quigley","Ryan Fisher","Lindsay Hall"}'::text[],
    2329,
    'https://teams.microsoft.com/l/meetup-join/19:meeting_ODBmZWFjMWYtMWIxYi00NmZmLTgyMDEtOWFiZWJhYWEwYzVh@thread.v2/0?context={"Tid":"3801011d-e732-48ee-be2a-e499b1a29ba4","Oid":"e804fbe9-a623-4d26-a887-992e62fb92d1"}',
    '{"id":"01KEDG6KENV9NNCD9C6F4PHPZ6","title":"Techmode+New North","summary":{"notes":"## **Sales Performance and Market Focus**\n\nThe team uncovered that their highest **win rate of 45%** occurs with deals under **100 stations**, while deals over **100 stations drop to a 22% win rate**, prompting a strategic shift toward smaller clients (14:58).\n\n- **Matthew Look** highlighted this unexpected shift in customer success, showing the need to reconsider their traditional enterprise focus on accounts over 100 stations.\n- They found the best segment is actually **1 to 50 stations**, with win rates declining incrementally above that.\n- This data calls for adjusting Google Ads and marketing efforts toward the **under 100 market**, especially **small and medium businesses (SMBs)**, to better reflect where they are winning.\n- The team agreed to build dedicated **SMB landing pages** and campaigns to target this segment, rather than rewriting the whole website immediately (18:50, 20:25, 27:45).\n\nMatthew also noted inconsistencies and mislabeling in deal data (e.g., a deal mislabeled as TechMode.Go), which Lindsay is fixing to improve accuracy for future analysis (16:17).\n\n## **Sales Process and Buyer Engagement**\n\nThe team discussed how to better communicate company legitimacy and value during sales, especially for larger deals.\n\n- A recent deal for **132 stations** showed that after presenting pricing, the prospect still asked about company size and reputation, indicating that current messaging may not stick (21:52).\n- **Ryan Fisher** suggested adding more visible **case studies and customer logos** to build trust quickly.\n- Matthew pointed out that the team already shares NPS scores (around **85 based on thousands of ratings**) and Better Business Bureau ratings but suspects the message may not resonate strongly (23:44).\n- The group considered flipping the sales script to lead with pricing and then reinforce company credibility to avoid losing prospects’ attention.\n- Colin emphasized tailoring conversations by starting with customer needs and then highlighting relevant features and credibility elements near the end of the sales cycle (26:27).\n\nThe overall takeaway is that sales messaging may need refinement to better hold buyers’ attention and answer their trust questions promptly.\n\n## **Marketing and Website Strategy**\n\nMarketing efforts will pivot to better address the SMB segment and improve SEO and AI content strategies.\n\n- The team is updating the **price hover page** and reducing header sizes per Lindsay’s notes, with campaigns ready to launch, including Microsoft Ads, price offer, virtual IP phone system, and MSP search campaigns (05:13, 06:37).\n- Matthew shared they are changing blog formats to include **executive summaries at the top** to improve AI-driven SEO on platforms like ChatGPT and Claude, enhancing content discoverability (07:31).\n- Lindsay is systematically reviewing the site to ensure consistent self-identification as a **UCaaS company**, which supports clearer positioning for search engines and customers (13:42).\n- The plan is to create **SMB-focused landing pages** linked from targeted Google Ads campaigns to better attract and convert small business leads without overhauling the entire site immediately (19:59, 27:45).\n- Colin confirmed an audit of Google Ads keywords is underway to refocus on the **under 100 stations market** as the primary target (30:48).\n\n## **Data Cleanup and Deal Validation**\n\nImproving CRM data quality is essential to understanding true sales performance.\n\n- Lindsay is working on correcting mislabeled deals and cleaning HubSpot records, especially for deals created around the HubSpot adoption period in early 2024 (16:21, 33:27).\n- The team agreed that leads without demos or meaningful engagement should not be marked as lost deals but rather as opportunities or discarded to avoid skewing win/loss rates (36:32).\n- This cleanup will help refine the actual win rate, which may rise from **22% to around 33%** once inaccurate entries are removed (37:41).\n- Matthew plans to follow up with sales reps for missing information and clarification to ensure data accuracy (36:18).\n\n## **Trademark and Brand Protection**\n\nThe company secured a broad **registered trademark** covering technology-related terms including UCaaS and AI, protecting their brand widely (29:01).\n\n- Matthew chose to apply broadly despite warnings, ensuring competitors cannot easily claim related technology terms.\n- Lindsay will coordinate swapping out the registered logos on the website to reflect this new status, with Colin managing the updates (28:45, 30:28).\n\n## **Next Steps and Priorities**\n\nThe team confirmed focus on the **under 100 stations market** moving forward, with marketing and sales efforts aligned accordingly (30:48).\n\n- Google Ads campaigns will be adjusted to emphasize this segment, with dedicated landing pages launching soon.\n- Data cleanup and deal validation will continue to ensure accurate sales metrics.\n- Sales messaging will be reviewed to improve buyer trust and engagement, especially for larger accounts.\n- Trademark updates and branding changes will be completed promptly to solidify market identity.","outline":null,"keywords":["SMB market","Google Ads campaigns","sales data analysis","AI content strategy","branding consistency","pricing presentation"],"overview":"- **Sales Focus Shift:** Focus on clients with under 100 stations due to a 45% win rate, compared to 22% for larger accounts.\n- **Marketing Alignment:** New campaigns for small and medium businesses will include dedicated landing pages and targeted Google Ads.\n- **Sales Messaging Improvement:** Refining messaging to enhance credibility and buyer trust, particularly for larger deals, is a priority.\n- **Data Quality Enhancement:** Cleaning up CRM data is crucial for accurate sales metrics; win rate may increase from 22% to 33%.\n- **Trademark Protection:** A broad registered trademark secures technology-related terms, strengthening brand defense against competitors.","action_items":"\n**Colin Costigan**\nImplement updates to the price hover page and tech mode go page as per Lindsay’s feedback (05:13)\nLaunch Microsoft ads campaign with current assets and budget, pending next week’s budget review (06:39)\nBegin development of SMB-focused landing page to target Google Ads traffic effectively (28:41)\nConduct audit of Google Ads keywords and campaigns to realign toward under-100 seat market segment (31:02)\nTake responsibility for swapping registered trademarked logos on website once Lindsay sends the updated files (30:37)\nPerform sales data cleanup in HubSpot for mislabeled deals and coordinate with sales team to confirm qualification of leads (36:07)\n\n**Lindsay Hall**\nContinue reviewing website pages to ensure consistent UCaaS branding and company references (13:42)\nProvide copy and updated registered trademark logos for website update (30:37)\nInvestigate and correct deal record inaccuracies in CRM, especially relating to unpitched or lost deals (30:37)\n\n**Matthew Look**\nContinue reviewing two-year sales data to verify win rates and deal qualification accuracy, specifically cleaning up dubious over-100 seat losses (14:04)\nShare insights and data with team to inform SMB landing page and campaign strategy (14:04)\nCoordinate with sales team (Mike and Kurt) post-call to get details on unclear deals and update CRM data accordingly (36:18)\n\n**Ryan Fisher**\nContribute perspective on developing case studies and logos to reinforce trust messaging during sales process (22:40)\n\n**All Participants**\nMonitor effectiveness of AI-generated blog content improvements focusing on executive summaries to improve SEO and AI relevance (07:31)\n"},"duration":38.81999969482422,"speakers":[{"id":0,"name":"Matthew Look"},{"id":1,"name":"Colin Costigan"},{"id":2,"name":"Christopher Quigley"},{"id":3,"name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"id":4,"name":"Lindsay Hall"}],"sentences":[{"text":"What''s up, gang?","index":0,"end_time":7.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":6.48,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"How''s it going?","index":1,"end_time":8.8,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":8.08,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Greetings.","index":2,"end_time":9.92,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":9.28,"speaker_name":"Christopher Quigley"},{"text":"I was gonna turn on my camera today, but this is what it looks like.","index":3,"end_time":14.6,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":11.84,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"So you''re an angel''s an angel.","index":4,"end_time":19.04,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":14.6,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"It''s like a 70s album cover.","index":5,"end_time":20.88,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":19.28,"speaker_name":"Christopher Quigley"},{"text":"Yeah, kind of.","index":6,"end_time":21.96,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":21.2,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"I wish.","index":7,"end_time":22.56,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":21.96,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Kind of like Ryan, the singer songwriter.","index":8,"end_time":25.76,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":22.64,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, yeah, exactly.","index":9,"end_time":29.89,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":26.05,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Maybe I''ll stick with it.","index":10,"end_time":31.65,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":30.53,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"Just don''t start saying like, baby, I'' ma want you.","index":11,"end_time":35.45,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":33.25,"speaker_name":"Christopher Quigley"},{"text":"Whatever.","index":12,"end_time":35.97,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":35.45,"speaker_name":"Christopher Quigley"},{"text":"Sing some Venture.","index":13,"end_time":37.53,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":36.61,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Let''s do some Ventura highway real quick.","index":14,"end_time":39.17,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":37.53,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Oh, that''s a good one.","index":15,"end_time":40.13,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":39.17,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"That is a good one.","index":16,"end_time":41.25,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":40.29,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"Of my yacht rock favorites.","index":17,"end_time":45.33,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":43.73,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"That is.","index":18,"end_time":45.89,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":45.41,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"That''s one of the best.","index":19,"end_time":46.77,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":45.89,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"My favorite doc one is Sailing by Christopher Cross.","index":20,"end_time":52.45,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":49.73,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"That''s my favorite one.","index":21,"end_time":53.21,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":52.45,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"On the dock.","index":22,"end_time":53.89,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":53.21,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Not the obvious one.","index":23,"end_time":56.13,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":55.17,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"Sitting on the dock of the bay.","index":24,"end_time":57.49,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":56.13,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"No, I don''t actually like that song.","index":25,"end_time":59.05,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":57.49,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"No.","index":26,"end_time":59.37,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":59.05,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"And that''s not really yacht rock either, but it just made me think.","index":27,"end_time":61.81,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":59.37,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"Yeah, that''s fair.","index":28,"end_time":62.53,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":61.81,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":29,"end_time":63.89,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":63.49,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"Sailing.","index":30,"end_time":64.41,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":63.89,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"That''s a good one.","index":31,"end_time":65.05,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":64.41,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"That''s a good one.","index":32,"end_time":65.81,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":65.05,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"I like some of the deep cuts.","index":33,"end_time":67.81,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":66.21,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"Cold Night.","index":34,"end_time":68.77,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":67.97,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"That''s a good one.","index":35,"end_time":69.73,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":68.77,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"I can''t remember who sings it, but there''s a lot of great yacht rock songs.","index":36,"end_time":74.37,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":70.049,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"Yeah, that was a good era of music.","index":37,"end_time":76.69,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":74.93,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"Yeah, that was a great era.","index":38,"end_time":78.61,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":77.25,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Usually when we out hitting on the golf simulator, that''s what we put on as yacht rock.","index":39,"end_time":82.69,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":78.85,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"It''s like it''s so agreeable for everybody.","index":40,"end_time":85.05,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":83.21,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"It''s the most agreeable music you can play.","index":41,"end_time":88.57,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":86.49,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Yeah, I don''t disagree.","index":42,"end_time":90.81,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":88.97,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"There''s actually a restaurant in Baltimore that''s Dock of the Bay is the name.","index":43,"end_time":97.29,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":92.49,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"They play yacht rock only I''ll have.","index":44,"end_time":101.41,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":98.65,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"To check and ask.","index":45,"end_time":102.25,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":101.41,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"How''s everybody doing?","index":46,"end_time":106.09,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":105.05,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Lovely, Colin, lovely.","index":47,"end_time":108.57,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":107.05,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Sorry, Chris, didn''t mean to cut you off.","index":48,"end_time":110.53,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":109.25,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Oh, that''s okay.","index":49,"end_time":111.57,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":110.61,"speaker_name":"Christopher Quigley"},{"text":"I was going to say there was a series of video shorts you can probably still find on YouTube called Yacht Rock and it was like about 10 or 12 of them.","index":50,"end_time":120.05,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":112.29,"speaker_name":"Christopher Quigley"},{"text":"And there were this hilarious send ups of yacht rock, of fictionalized versions of hall and Oates and the guy who was the center of the yacht rock movement, Coco, whatever his name was.","index":51,"end_time":131.97,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":120.21,"speaker_name":"Christopher Quigley"},{"text":"Anyways, it''s.","index":52,"end_time":133.53,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":132.61,"speaker_name":"Christopher Quigley"},{"text":"If you ever get bored and you.","index":53,"end_time":135.01,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":133.53,"speaker_name":"Christopher Quigley"},{"text":"Got like, isn''t that worth.","index":54,"end_time":136.47,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":135.01,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"I think that''s where the whole thing started.","index":55,"end_time":137.91,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":136.47,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"Wasn''t it on YouTube?","index":56,"end_time":139.11,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":137.91,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"Yeah, it wasn''t.","index":57,"end_time":140.39,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":139.43,"speaker_name":"Christopher Quigley"},{"text":"It wasn''t YouTube at first.","index":58,"end_time":141.31,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":140.39,"speaker_name":"Christopher Quigley"},{"text":"It was like channel 101 or something like that.","index":59,"end_time":143.07,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":141.31,"speaker_name":"Christopher Quigley"},{"text":"But it all moved.","index":60,"end_time":144.23,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":143.07,"speaker_name":"Christopher Quigley"},{"text":"Moved to YouTube because it predated YouTube actually a little bit, so.","index":61,"end_time":149.03,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":144.23,"speaker_name":"Christopher Quigley"},{"text":"But it''s hilarious.","index":62,"end_time":150.31,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":149.35,"speaker_name":"Christopher Quigley"},{"text":"I watch it every now and then just because it still makes me laugh.","index":63,"end_time":153.43,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":150.31,"speaker_name":"Christopher Quigley"},{"text":"So isn''t There a thing in Michigan where whenever all four teams are playing at the same time, there''s like a song that everyone sings.","index":64,"end_time":161.51,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":153.99,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I hallucinating.","index":65,"end_time":163.75,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":162.87,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, I don''t know about that.","index":66,"end_time":165.31,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":164.15,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"I think so, man.","index":67,"end_time":166.23,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":165.31,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"I don''t know.","index":68,"end_time":166.91,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":166.31,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"I don''t know that one.","index":69,"end_time":167.91,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":166.91,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"Sorry.","index":70,"end_time":168.63,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":168.15,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"Gotta stay off those drugs, Colin.","index":71,"end_time":170.95,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":169.11,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Hitting that baby formula a little too hard, bro.","index":72,"end_time":174.63,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":172.47,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"That''s not.","index":73,"end_time":175.63,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":175.03,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"That does sound like a Michigan thing, but I don''t know it.","index":74,"end_time":178.39,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":175.63,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"I saw it in like a. I don''t know if you guys ever watched Detroiters.","index":75,"end_time":181.99,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":178.71,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I know of it.","index":76,"end_time":184.47,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":183.51,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"Yeah, I know of it too.","index":77,"end_time":185.67,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":184.47,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":78,"end_time":186.15,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":185.67,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":79,"end_time":187.92,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":187.6,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Very, very stupid.","index":80,"end_time":188.92,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":187.92,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Funny.","index":81,"end_time":189.36,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":188.92,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I love how the two people who watch it aren''t from Detroit or aren''t from Michigan.","index":82,"end_time":193.4,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":189.68,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Yeah, well, we live in.","index":83,"end_time":194.28,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":193.4,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"I don''t know what you''re talking about.","index":84,"end_time":195.36,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":194.28,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Yeah, we don''t need to see it.","index":85,"end_time":197.44,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":195.36,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":86,"end_time":200.96,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":200.4,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"I''m fighting everything today, guys.","index":87,"end_time":203.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":201.52,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"So I am just not winning.","index":88,"end_time":207.6,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":203.28,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Like, under the weather.","index":89,"end_time":209.84,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":208.8,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"No, just can''t.","index":90,"end_time":211.4,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":210.24,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Like everything.","index":91,"end_time":211.88,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":211.4,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"I''m fighting everything.","index":92,"end_time":212.72,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":211.88,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Like everything I''m trying to do.","index":93,"end_time":214.16,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":212.8,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"I got Claude going right now and it''s just freaking circling.","index":94,"end_time":217.76,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":214.16,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"I got Chat GPT doing all sorts of dumb.","index":95,"end_time":221.2,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":217.76,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"I got every salesperson doing their own dumb.","index":96,"end_time":223.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":221.28,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Got.","index":97,"end_time":225.36,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":224.96,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Everybody''s just yanking my chain.","index":98,"end_time":229.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":225.52,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Colin, I''m not too.","index":99,"end_time":231.2,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":229.28,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"I''m way far from paradise.","index":100,"end_time":232.72,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":231.2,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"It''s a long way for me.","index":101,"end_time":234,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":232.72,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"The wind is not right.","index":102,"end_time":236,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":234.8,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"And I''ve been monitoring Down Detector for the last two days just because I''ve been seeing weird issues.","index":103,"end_time":240.72,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":236.16,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Google teams Cloudflare aws.","index":104,"end_time":246.48,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":243.84,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Well, someone keeps messing with the Internet.","index":105,"end_time":249.6,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":247.6,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Cloudflare basically front ends, all of it.","index":106,"end_time":251.84,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":249.6,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"And everything''s down.","index":107,"end_time":254.24,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":253.28,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"One of the lava lamps is out.","index":108,"end_time":257.68,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":256.24,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Yeah, exactly.","index":109,"end_time":259.28,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":258.4,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":110,"end_time":260.32,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":260,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I mean, it happened twice last year where they just kind of unplugged the Internet.","index":111,"end_time":263.12,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":260.32,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah.","index":112,"end_time":264.44,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":263.44,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"Right at the end.","index":113,"end_time":265.2,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":264.44,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"I mean, it felt like it was both in the end of the year.","index":114,"end_time":268.25,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":265.2,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":115,"end_time":269.21,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":268.73,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"But yeah.","index":116,"end_time":270.73,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":269.53,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Yeah, I''ve been just scrolling through this.","index":117,"end_time":272.97,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":271.37,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Fine.","index":118,"end_time":273.61,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":273.05,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Yeah, there''s your Claude aws.","index":119,"end_time":277.53,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":274.65,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Whoa, whoa, whoa.","index":120,"end_time":280.37,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":279.69,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"Roblox is down.","index":121,"end_time":281.45,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":280.37,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"God damn it.","index":122,"end_time":282.65,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":281.53,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Amazing news.","index":123,"end_time":285.05,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":284.01,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Just a blip, Matt.","index":124,"end_time":286.57,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":285.53,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"Just a blip.","index":125,"end_time":287.21,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":286.57,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"Oh, okay.","index":126,"end_time":287.97,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":287.29,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"All right.","index":127,"end_time":288.29,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":287.97,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"You''re fine.","index":128,"end_time":288.97,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":288.29,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"Me and my 12 year old friends are all going to hop on Roblox later tonight.","index":129,"end_time":293.37,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":289.69,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"What cracks me up about Down Detector though, Colin, and kind of how everything is is that all the graphs are the fucking same.","index":130,"end_time":301.43,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":294.01,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"Do you know what I mean?","index":131,"end_time":304.07,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":303.19,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"Graph?","index":132,"end_time":307.51,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":306.95,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"Yeah, Kind of.","index":133,"end_time":309.83,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":308.15,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"Kind of shows you how the whole thing''s set up now.","index":134,"end_time":311.75,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":309.83,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":135,"end_time":312.47,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":311.91,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"There''s just one server with one guy sitting in there with a big red button.","index":136,"end_time":316.79,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":313.67,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":137,"end_time":322.03,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":321.43,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So we did update the price hover page.","index":138,"end_time":324.11,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":322.03,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I''m not sure if you guys have seen that.","index":139,"end_time":325.87,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":324.11,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I. I was out the last couple days of last week for annual planning and then I was sick.","index":140,"end_time":329.87,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":325.87,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So I haven''t been as much on the email, but we did update the headlines and Lindsay, to your note, reduced the size of this header area here and made every other update that you guys had left comments on and one.","index":141,"end_time":341.07,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":329.87,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"That I wanted to, by the way.","index":142,"end_time":342.23,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":341.07,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"She''s not.","index":143,"end_time":343.35,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":342.63,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"No, she''s not.","index":144,"end_time":344.67,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":343.67,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Okay, we''ll look for.","index":145,"end_time":346.07,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":344.67,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We''ll look for a different one.","index":146,"end_time":347.59,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":346.55,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And then Lindsay, one of the sections that you wanted us to just come up with new content for was.","index":147,"end_time":353.63,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":349.27,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Right.","index":148,"end_time":353.91,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":353.63,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, that''s Matt''s guy right there.","index":149,"end_time":357.81,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":356.13,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"It looks great.","index":150,"end_time":359.89,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":359.01,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"It looks great.","index":151,"end_time":360.85,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":360.05,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"This is being funny.","index":152,"end_time":365.49,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":364.37,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":153,"end_time":366.97,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":366.53,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And then we do have this going to the tech mode go page.","index":154,"end_time":369.89,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":366.97,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I wanted to see if we wanted to switch that to something else.","index":155,"end_time":372.53,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":369.89,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I mean, I''m good with that.","index":156,"end_time":375.61,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":374.45,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"The tech mode go page tells you what''s included, that''s for sure.","index":157,"end_time":379.17,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":375.61,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"That was the thought process.","index":158,"end_time":381.34,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":380.54,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I''m not upset about driving traffic to that page.","index":159,"end_time":384.46,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":382.06,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"If people are going to leave our landing page, I''m not upset about them going to that page, you know.","index":160,"end_time":389.02,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":384.46,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":161,"end_time":389.82,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":389.26,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay, great.","index":162,"end_time":391.74,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":391.02,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"So are there any other changes before then?","index":163,"end_time":394.62,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":392.86,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We can get the Microsoft ads campaign going.","index":164,"end_time":397.02,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":394.62,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"No, we can get it going.","index":165,"end_time":398.38,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":397.34,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"All right, perfect.","index":166,"end_time":400.22,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":399.18,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And then we also have the price offer campaign live and the virtual IP phone system as well and the MSP search campaign and just wanted to check budget there.","index":167,"end_time":414.09,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":401.58,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We set preliminary at $20 a day but wanted to check with you guys if that''s reasonable or if you wanted to change it.","index":168,"end_time":420.65,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":414.09,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I haven''t thought about it.","index":169,"end_time":423.21,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":422.249,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"I don''t know.","index":170,"end_time":423.85,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":423.21,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"So can we mark that down to come back to.","index":171,"end_time":425.77,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":423.93,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Yeah, of course.","index":172,"end_time":426.81,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":425.93,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Next week.","index":173,"end_time":428.17,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":427.45,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Yeah, sure thing.","index":174,"end_time":430.01,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":428.81,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And then the rest of the agenda was just dedicated to whatever outcome of your guys meeting after we talked last week around thought leadership and SEO and AI generated or not AI generated but AI overviews and getting ranked in ChatGPT and those types of search engines.","index":175,"end_time":449.09,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":430.41,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Well, I mean we are changing the format a little bit for our blogs for AI and AI.","index":176,"end_time":456.45,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":451.09,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"AI intent.","index":177,"end_time":457.41,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":456.45,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"What I have learned, and I know I''m going to say this accounts being like, yeah, I already knew that.","index":178,"end_time":463.46,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":459.89,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"But it seems chatgpt and Claude both agree that in our blog post it wants a summary of the entire article at the very top of the blog post.","index":179,"end_time":475.61,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":464.57,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Yeah, like an executive overview.","index":180,"end_time":478.57,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":477.05,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, Yep, exactly that.","index":181,"end_time":480.65,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":478.65,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"It uses that summary for AI intent.","index":182,"end_time":483.53,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":480.65,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"So your first one''s coming over right now and this is what I''m fighting Right now, Lindsay and Claude.","index":183,"end_time":488.65,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":484.73,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Okay.","index":184,"end_time":489.13,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":488.65,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"I always love when it''s like, I asked it to do something and I''m like, you didn''t do it.","index":185,"end_time":492.33,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":489.33,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"It''s like, oh, you know what?","index":186,"end_time":493.13,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":492.33,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"You''re exactly right.","index":187,"end_time":493.97,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":493.13,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"I didn''t.","index":188,"end_time":494.77,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":494.13,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"And then it''s like, okay, but are you going to.","index":189,"end_time":497.97,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":495.89,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Yeah, you MF her.","index":190,"end_time":499.85,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":498.37,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And then it works a little faster.","index":191,"end_time":500.93,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":499.85,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Like you''re as fucking bad as employees.","index":192,"end_time":502.69,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":500.93,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"That''s exactly what I was thinking, Matt.","index":193,"end_time":505.01,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":503.25,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"Wasn''t it supposed to fix that?","index":194,"end_time":509.65,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":508.13,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"Exactly.","index":195,"end_time":511.09,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":510.05,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"So, I mean, that''s.","index":196,"end_time":515.41,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":514.45,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"We''re slowly and steadily working on that so that you''ll see more and more of that as we continue to write more and more blogs.","index":197,"end_time":522.13,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":515.65,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"It''s not worth going back and fixing some.","index":198,"end_time":524.13,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":522.13,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"I might go back and fix some of the.","index":199,"end_time":526.37,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":524.45,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Maybe the Ring Central ones I might change just because that seems to be a hot topic for us that we''re kind of going after right now.","index":200,"end_time":533.89,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":526.61,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":201,"end_time":534.69,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":534.21,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"So that might be worth rewriting a little bit.","index":202,"end_time":537.57,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":535.49,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Someone talked to me about how they were using Ring Central and I was going to recommend you, but they are a one person team.","index":203,"end_time":542.77,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":537.89,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And I was like, probably not worth.","index":204,"end_time":544.05,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":542.77,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Dude.","index":205,"end_time":544.69,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":544.37,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Oh, my God, you guys, this is.","index":206,"end_time":546.49,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":544.69,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Last week we got a Google lead came in for a roofing company.","index":207,"end_time":550.13,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":546.49,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"You guys, probably my.","index":208,"end_time":551.29,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":550.37,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Colin''s like, yeah, I saw it.","index":209,"end_time":552.25,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":551.29,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"I know.","index":210,"end_time":552.69,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":552.25,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"And so I''m like, I''m gonna.","index":211,"end_time":555.53,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":553.49,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"I had a minute.","index":212,"end_time":556.17,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":555.53,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"So I just looked it up.","index":213,"end_time":557.17,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":556.17,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Like 75 to 200 employees.","index":214,"end_time":558.93,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":557.25,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"I''m like, dang.","index":215,"end_time":559.45,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":558.93,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Pretty good.","index":216,"end_time":559.97,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":559.45,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Went to their webpage.","index":217,"end_time":560.97,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":559.97,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Webpage is pretty well built out.","index":218,"end_time":562.29,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":560.97,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"I''m like, all right, this is pretty good.","index":219,"end_time":564.25,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":563.09,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"So we get on the call with them.","index":220,"end_time":565.21,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":564.25,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"He''s like, I want to do this, I want to do that.","index":221,"end_time":566.69,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":565.21,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text