hey probably all got rounded up in Chicago, Chris.","index":237,"end_time":597.45,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":594.89,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Probably.","index":238,"end_time":598.71,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":598.31,"speaker_name":"Christopher Quigley"},{"text":"Bummer.","index":239,"end_time":600.87,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":600.23,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"It was a roofing company out of Chicago.","index":240,"end_time":603.03,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":601.27,"speaker_name":"Christopher Quigley"},{"text":"No, it wasn''t.","index":241,"end_time":604.15,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":603.35,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"I just came out.","index":242,"end_time":605.59,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":604.15,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"We haven''t had Chicago.","index":243,"end_time":608.63,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":606.47,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"We haven''t had ICE yet in Detroit.","index":244,"end_time":610.39,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":608.63,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"I don''t know that that would go over well in Detroit, to be honest.","index":245,"end_time":613.11,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":610.87,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"They should be scared.","index":246,"end_time":614.55,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":613.43,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Yeah, I know.","index":247,"end_time":615.75,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":614.95,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"They should be scared to come to me.","index":248,"end_time":617.43,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":615.83,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Some pretty big gun toting over there.","index":249,"end_time":620.07,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":617.67,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, I''ve been thinking about that a lot, too.","index":250,"end_time":622.95,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":620.07,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"Like, when and if is it going to happen?","index":251,"end_time