":0,"start_time":888.62,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"That is a little bit mind boggling to us.","index":362,"end_time":898.15,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":895.91,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Yeah, it''s definitely a shift for us, without a doubt.","index":363,"end_time":901.27,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":898.23,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"So, I mean, our close rate at under 100 is probably 45% I think is what it was.","index":364,"end_time":908.63,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":902.39,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"We go above 100, it''s 22.","index":365,"end_time":910.87,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":908.79,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"I have to imagine some of those losses are just competitor to bring central or something like that.","index":366,"end_time":918.07,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":911.83,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, the data might be a little skewed, Ryan.","index":367,"end_time":921.19,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":918.39,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"I''m kind of diving into it a little bit and let me give you guys, I have it all in chat GPT so I''m able to parse the data pretty quick.","index":368,"end_time":929.59,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":921.19,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"But like one of.","index":369,"end_time":931.99,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":931.11,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Got an Excel add on too.","index":370,"end_time":933.75,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":932.31,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, Claude and I aren''t getting along.","index":371,"end_time":937.83,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":935.75,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"They''re taking a break.","index":372,"end_time":940.71,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":939.75,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"We are taking a break.","index":373,"end_time":942.23,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":941.19,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"We''re kind of on.","index":374,"end_ti