37,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":981.17,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"I''m going to dig it, I''m going to find it and I''m going to fix it so that we can get better data.","index":389,"end_time":986.45,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":982.37,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"So it might not be as bad as what we think.","index":390,"end_time":989.77,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":987.81,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"You know, there''s not a lot of those deals.","index":391,"end_time":991.57,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":989.77,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"So if you fix two of them, it does change it a little bit.","index":392,"end_time":995.17,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":992.45,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"She can''t have that many, right?","index":393,"end_time":999.01,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":997.65,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"I''ll figure it out.","index":394,"end_time":999.89,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":999.01,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"No, she didn''t.","index":395,"end_time":1000.85,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1000.05,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"But anyways.","index":396,"end_time":1001.49,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1000.85,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"So anyways, what we''re learning is that we win pretty well under 100.","index":397,"end_time":1005.78,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1001.94,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"That has not been what our thoughts about who we are have been ever.","index":398,"end_time":1009.94,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1006.5,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"You know, we''re used to interacting with IT teams, we''re used to interacting with C levels, we''re used to doing all that stuff.","index":399,"end_time":1017.78,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1012.5,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"But that isn''t where we''re winning.","index":400,"end_time":1019.46,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1018.02,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Right.","index":401,"end_time":1020.26,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1019.86,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"What does that mean?","index":402,"end_time":1021.54,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1020.5,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"And what do we do different or what do we want to do different in Google Ads based on the knowledge that we have there.","index":403,"end_time":1029.17,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1021.86,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"And if you want to get very specific, under 50 the win rate is better than over 50.","index":404,"end_time":1033.81,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1029.25,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"The 1 to 50 is our highest win rate.","index":405,"end_time":1036.37,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1034.61,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"50 to 100 is a little lower over 100.","index":406,"end_time":1039.97,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1036.85,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"It falls off a cliff basically.","index":407,"end_time":1041.25,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1039.97,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Right.","index":408,"end_time":1042.05,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1041.65,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So even before talking about tech mode specifically, I want to talk about the industries.","index":409,"end_time":1047.09,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1043.33,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Is this a shift you guys are seeing?","index":410,"end_time":1049.41,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1047.17,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Obviously you''re looking at your data but I mean even the conversation you just had where a company has, you know, hundreds of people registered as employees but they maybe have downsized their team of who actually gets lines or seats, do you think that''s maybe going on?","index":411,"end_time":1063.45,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1049.81,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"No, I Don''t think that that''s the case.","index":412,"end_time":1065.49,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1064.01,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"The one I just talked about is, you know, I was cautious because it was a roofing company that it was going to be small.","index":413,"end_time":1070.65,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1065.49,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"So I think it was bad information and seamless.","index":414,"end_time":1073.289,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1071.21,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Or you just have a ton of field workers.","index":415,"end_time":1074.81,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1073.289,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Right, right.","index":416,"end_time":1075.85,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1074.89,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"So field workers don''t get phone seats or any of that shit.","index":417,"end_time":1078.97,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1075.85,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Yeah, gotcha.","index":418,"end_time":1081.21,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1079.13,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Well, what I think it means is tailoring the content of the website to speak less to enterprise and more to like we serve.","index":419,"end_time":1088.72,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1081.45,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"You know, Joe, who runs this company.","index":420,"end_time":1091.28,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1088.96,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I don''t disagree.","index":421,"end_time":1093.08,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1091.92,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"I hate that.","index":422,"end_time":1093.8,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1093.08,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"I hate the thought of that.","index":423,"end_time":1094.88,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1093.8,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"It makes me want to cringe because I freaking hate it.","index":424,"end_time":1097.92,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1094.88,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"But I don''t think you''re wrong.","index":425,"end_time":1099.36,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1098.08,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Yeah, well, I think, I don''t think.","index":426,"end_time":1101.44,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1099.76,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"It''S a hard reality, unfortunately, Colin.","index":427,"end_time":1103.68,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1101.44,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":428,"end_time":1104,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1103.68,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"And I don''t know if it''s an overnight, like, you know, rewrite the entire homepage or if we start with some landing pages more dedicated to it and see how those go and then.","index":429,"end_time":1112.16,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1104,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, and that''s my thought.","index":430,"end_time":1113.4,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1112.32,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"I think we start with some landing pages more dedicated to it.","index":431,"end_time":1115.92,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1113.4,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":432,"end_time":1116.54,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1116.22,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"So, Ryan, you know, because we may have to.","index":433,"end_time":1120.94,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1118.94,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Well, I, I agree with you, Matt.","index":434,"end_time":1125.5,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1123.5,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"I think in the short term we got to play to our strength.","index":435,"end_time":1130.38,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1127.66,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"Right?","index":436,"end_time":1130.66,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1130.38,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Because I think, Matt, we got to figure out if we go for the big, bigger business going forward and it.","index":437,"end_time":1137.62,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1130.66,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"And if so, how.","index":438,"end_time":1138.7,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1137.62,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"And we don''t necessarily have that answer right today.","index":439,"end_time":1143.04,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1139.02,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"But, you know, it''s something that we.","index":440,"end_time":1146.12,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1143.84,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"Need to tell us more about.","index":441,"end_time":1147.2,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1146.12,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"The safe bet for us is if we do custom landing pages for SMB, we don''t change our whole website.","index":442,"end_time":1153.36,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1147.6,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"We drive Google traffic to specific web pages for SMB.","index":443,"end_time":1157.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1153.76,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"And then now can we market to under 100 and can we specify that as something within Google Ads?","index":444,"end_time":1166.56,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1158.8,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"It''s really just going to be reliant on like the signals that they pick up over time.","index":445,"end_time":1171.08,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1167.52,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"It''s not like an audience that they have ready of those businesses.","index":446,"end_time":1173.51,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1171.08,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Gotcha.","index":447,"end_time":1175.98,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1175.42,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"And what I will say is, you know, we''ve probably steered some of those people away in other campaigns where we talk about like a minimum seat number.","index":448,"end_time":1183.98,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1177.42,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"You''re not wrong.","index":449,"end_time":1185.58,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1184.7,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"You''re not wrong.","index":450,"end_time":1188.06,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1187.18,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"But I mean, I went through two years of data, so I mean, I have.","index":451,"end_time":1194.54,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1190.38,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Is it a lot of data?","index":452,"end_time":1196.1,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1195.02,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"It''s not a ton of data, but it is all the data for two years.","index":453,"end_time":1198.86,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1196.1,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Right.","index":454,"end_time":1199.59,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1199.35,"speaker_name":"Christopher Quigley"},{"text":"So, you know, so I think, I think the thought is maybe we should look to build an SMB page.","index":455,"end_time":1207.19,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1200.71,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Landing page.","index":456,"end_time":1208.87,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1207.99,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Agreed.","index":457,"end_time":1210.87,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1210.23,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"I agree with that.","index":458,"end_time":1212.23,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1211.27,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay.","index":459,"end_time":1213.27,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1212.63,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"Sorry, Matt.","index":460,"end_time":1216.67,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1215.99,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"If I went a little bit on the Other side of that.","index":461,"end_time":1218.99,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1216.67,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"But if we''re just talking about landing the landing page, then, yeah, obviously, that seems like a great initial.","index":462,"end_time":1225.12,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1218.99,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"It''s an easy.","index":463,"end_time":1225.84,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1225.12,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"It''s an actually easy fix.","index":464,"end_time":1227.16,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1225.84,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":465,"end_time":1227.44,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1227.16,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"It''s an easy, easy way to deal with that situation.","index":466,"end_time":1229.84,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1227.44,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"It''s an easy, quick fix.","index":467,"end_time":1231.68,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1230.4,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":468,"end_time":1232.24,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1231.76,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"Yep.","index":469,"end_time":1232.72,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1232.24,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Is what I''m.","index":470,"end_time":1234.68,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1233.92,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"I''m thinking now.","index":471,"end_time":1235.36,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1234.68,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"I don''t say we give up on over 100.","index":472,"end_time":1236.84,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1235.36,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"I think we just got to rethink why and what we''re doing differently.","index":473,"end_time":1239.76,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1236.84,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"So I''m going to give you guys, here''s a.","index":474,"end_time":1241.48,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1240.08,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Here is something interesting, actually.","index":475,"end_time":1243.04,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1241.48,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"This is extremely interesting.","index":476,"end_time":1244.24,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1243.04,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Ryan and Lindsay, based on the conversation we had, and Colin, you can ride along on this one.","index":477,"end_time":1248.96,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1244.72,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"So we had a.","index":478,"end_time":1251.56,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1249.92,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"My God, it''s still going.","index":479,"end_time":1254.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1252.44,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Claude''s still going.","index":480,"end_time":1255.56,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1254.44,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Let me look at Kurt.","index":481,"end_time":1258.76,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1257.72,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"So we proposed a deal today that we got.","index":482,"end_time":1266.12,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1260.28,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"I don''t know if it came through 3Cx or whatever it was, but basically it''s like 132 stations, so it''s above the hundred.","index":483,"end_time":1278.29,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1266.999,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"So we presented the new pricing format, which Lindsey and Ryan, you guys are both familiar with.","index":484,"end_time":1284.29,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1280.21,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"It was a quick call.","index":485,"end_time":1286.05,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1285.25,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"We basically.","index":486,"end_time":1286.61,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1286.05,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"I''m like.","index":487,"end_time":1287.01,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1286.61,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Kurt''s like, what do we do?","index":488,"end_time":1287.85,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1287.01,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"I''m like, let''s go through about who we are a little bit to start with, Talk about NPS score, talk about our Better Business Bureau rating, talk about how long we''ve been doing this.","index":489,"end_time":1294.93,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1287.85,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Let''s sell ourselves, knowing we have to make.","index":490,"end_time":1297.41,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1295.17,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"We have to add legitimacy to who we are.","index":491,"end_time":1299.85,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1297.65,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Right.","index":492,"end_time":1300.21,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1299.85,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"We know that based on some of the information we''ve kind of uncovered on ourselves.","index":493,"end_time":1305.19,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1300.29,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"So we did that to start with.","index":494,"end_time":1307.23,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1306.07,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"We did not spend much time on it.","index":495,"end_time":1308.79,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1307.23,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"We spent maybe 10 minutes on it because we did not want to lose interest.","index":496,"end_time":1311.83,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1308.79,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Then we delve into the pricing.","index":497,"end_time":1314.23,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1312.79,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Customer did not seem appalled by the new pricing, the new way we presented the pricing.","index":498,"end_time":1319.35,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1315.11,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"And then they ask, so can you tell me a little bit about who you are?","index":499,"end_time":1324.07,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1319.83,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Was after we presented the pricing.","index":500,"end_time":1326.47,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1324.47,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Interesting.","index":501,"end_time":1328.39,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1327.75,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"How many of these instances do you have installed?","index":502,"end_time":1330.92,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1328.76,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"You know, so it made me think, like, were you not fucking paying attention for the first part of this?","index":503,"end_time":1337.72,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1331.4,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"So I would take it as a buyer''s intent.","index":504,"end_time":1340.8,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1338.44,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Right?","index":505,"end_time":1341.08,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1340.8,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Because they were like, all right, this is kind of in line with what we''re doing now.","index":506,"end_time":1343.84,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1341.08,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Let''s talk about a little bit about who you are and whether we trust you.","index":507,"end_time":1346.44,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1343.84,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Right.","index":508,"end_time":1346.84,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1346.44,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"But we did cover that.","index":509,"end_time":1348.92,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1347.56,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"We covered that in the initial call we had with them.","index":510,"end_time":1353,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1350.52,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"We covered it at the beginning of this call, but they still ask that question.","index":511,"end_time":1357.78,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1353.16,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"So.","index":512,"end_time":1358.58,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1358.18,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"Where do you inject that?","index":513,"end_time":1362.94,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1360.34,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Or how do you make that more relevant?","index":514,"end_time":1366.54,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1362.94,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Right.","index":515,"end_time":1366.9,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1366.54,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"How do we make it rememberable or something that sticks?","index":516,"end_time":1370.98,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1366.98,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Because apparently it didn''t stick.","index":517,"end_time":1372.34,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1370.98,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"I think it goes to.","index":518,"end_time":1374.9,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1373.46,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"And I''m not saying we''re in a great position for this right now, but I think it goes to case studies and logos of who we.","index":519,"end_time":1382.3,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1375.06,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"Who our customers are, potentially.","index":520,"end_time":1384.26,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1382.3,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":521,"end_time":1388.3,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1388.06,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"I don''t disagree.","index":522,"end_time":1389.18,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1388.3,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"You know, like as a starting point or something along those lines.","index":523,"end_time":1392.98,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1389.5,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"Because you just see, that''s what everybody does.","index":524,"end_time":1394.74,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1392.98,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"Right.","index":525,"end_time":1395.1,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1394.74,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"But we do have logos.","index":526,"end_time":1396.62,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1395.26,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"You add logos, you add case studies.","index":527,"end_time":1399.18,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1397.26,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"Yeah, we do have logos in our.","index":528,"end_time":1401.02,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1399.26,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Provided to them first.","index":529,"end_time":1403.3,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1402.22,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":530,"end_time":1403.74,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1403.3,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":531,"end_time":1404.26,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1403.82,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"I guess I''m just spitballing.","index":532,"end_time":1405.74,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1404.26,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":533,"end_time":1406.98,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1406.54,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"I don''t know.","index":534,"end_time":1407.58,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1406.98,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"But I don''t.","index":535,"end_time":1409.78,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1409.1,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Apparently we''re not getting that across.","index":536,"end_time":1411.26,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1409.78,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"And even then when we make a.","index":537,"end_time":1412.57,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1411.69,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Point, that''s surprising to me because I''ve heard that spiel so much that how is that not coming across?","index":538,"end_time":1418.89,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1412.57,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"I don''t know.","index":539,"end_time":1419.81,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1418.97,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"That''s.","index":540,"end_time":1420.17,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1419.81,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"That''s interesting to me.","index":541,"end_time":1421.29,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1420.17,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"I don''t know.","index":542,"end_time":1425.13,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1424.41,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"And maybe we''re not defining NPS better enough.","index":543,"end_time":1429.05,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1426.17,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Maybe we need to be like, listen, we have.","index":544,"end_time":1431.21,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1429.29,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Our NPS score is an 85 or 86, whatever the hell it is.","index":545,"end_time":1434.81,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1431.85,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"And that''s based on 4,000 ratings or how many we have within.","index":546,"end_time":1438.73,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1435.05,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Yep.","index":547,"end_time":1439.9,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1439.58,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"You know, it''s thousands, but.","index":548,"end_time":1442.26,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1439.9,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"Yeah, thousands.","index":549,"end_time":1443.06,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1442.26,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Not exactly how many, but yeah, you.","index":550,"end_time":1446.1,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1443.06,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"Know, maybe we need to.","index":551,"end_time":1447.18,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1446.1,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Maybe that would legitimize that a little bit more.","index":552,"end_time":1449.3,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1447.26,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"I don''t know.","index":553,"end_time":1449.66,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1449.3,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"I guess I don''t have any thoughts on this.","index":554,"end_time":1451.02,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1449.66,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"I was kicking this out to the group because it is only one.","index":555,"end_time":1453.58,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1451.02,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Right.","index":556,"end_time":1453.9,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1453.58,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"So I don''t know that we make a change based on that.","index":557,"end_time":1455.74,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1453.9,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"No, but it''s something we see coming.","index":558,"end_time":1457.5,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1455.9,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"Up more and more.","index":559,"end_time":1458.22,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1457.5,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Like, how do we plan based on the information we had was sell ourselves a little bit, don''t oversell it so we don''t lose them and then present pricing.","index":560,"end_time":1467.39,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1458.22,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"But then he asked the same question.","index":561,"end_time":1468.71,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1467.39,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Which makes.","index":562,"end_time":1473.03,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1472.39,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"It''s two things.","index":563,"end_time":1473.83,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1473.11,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"He wasn''t paying attention or what we said wasn''t what he was looking for necessarily.","index":564,"end_time":1479.59,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1473.83,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"When.","index":565,"end_time":1479.91,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1479.59,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"When he says tell us about ourselves, he''s maybe means something else.","index":566,"end_time":1484.55,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1479.99,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":567,"end_time":1485.35,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1485.03,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"And it was.","index":568,"end_time":1485.71,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1485.35,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"It was.","index":569,"end_time":1486.07,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1485.71,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"It wasn''t exactly tell us about yourself.","index":570,"end_time":1488.11,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1486.07,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"It was more like, how many of these instances do you have installed?","index":571,"end_time":1490.95,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1488.11,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"You know, how many people do you have on staff?","index":572,"end_time":1492.82,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1491.3,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"What''s your.","index":573,"end_time":1493.78,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1493.22,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"What.","index":574,"end_time":1494.1,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1493.78,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"What do you look like?","index":575,"end_time":1495.22,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1494.1,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"You know, what''s your support look like?","index":576,"end_time":1496.74,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1495.22,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Blah, blah, blah.","index":577,"end_time":1497.66,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1496.74,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Those are the types of questions that he asked.","index":578,"end_time":1499.22,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1497.66,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"I think we used to have like a hot sheet with that information.","index":579,"end_time":1506.5,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1504.26,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"And I don''t.","index":580,"end_time":1507.139,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1506.58,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"We don''t really give that out anymore.","index":581,"end_time":1509.54,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1507.139,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Right.","index":582,"end_time":1509.86,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1509.54,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"We do.","index":583,"end_time":1510.7,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1510.26,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"We have something we should.","index":584,"end_time":1511.62,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1510.7,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"It''s on.","index":585,"end_time":1512.02,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1511.62,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"It''s on our.","index":586,"end_time":1512.82,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1512.1,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Isn''t it on our selling uphill dock.","index":587,"end_time":1516.5,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1513.06,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"We don''t talk about, like, how many texts we have or how many people we have, you know, on staff.","index":588,"end_time":1522.23,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1518.27,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"We don''t address those in the document.","index":589,"end_time":1524.67,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1522.23,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Yeah, I don''t know that we should.","index":590,"end_time":1526.27,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1524.83,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"No, I don''t think it.","index":591,"end_time":1527.75,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1526.83,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"I don''t think it supports our cause necessarily.","index":592,"end_time":1530.11,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1527.75,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"Right.","index":593,"end_time":1530.95,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1530.59,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Because all it tells you is that we''re a small company, which isn''t a bad thing, but maybe that''s where people are getting cold feet.","index":594,"end_time":1538.63,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1530.95,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"I don''t know.","index":595,"end_time":1539.23,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1538.63,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Anyways, that was my thought.","index":596,"end_time":1541.75,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1540.67,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"There was my chant with you guys on.","index":597,"end_time":1544.91,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1541.75,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, yeah.","index":598,"end_time":1545.95,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1545.15,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"No, I mean, that''s.","index":599,"end_time":1546.79,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1545.95,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"That is interesting information for sure.","index":600,"end_time":1548.51,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1546.79,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"Yep.","index":601,"end_time":1549.47,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1548.91,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"I mean, when I usually approach a sales conversation, I. I start with who they are and, and kind of give them the opportunity to dive into what they''re looking for, what their business is about.","index":602,"end_time":1563.39,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1551.79,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And then I kind of tailor based on that.","index":603,"end_time":1566.39,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1564.19,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"You know, you go in with like, these are the features we want to talk about and everything.","index":604,"end_time":1569.71,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1566.39,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"You can kind of tailor exactly what you, you know, amplify of that based on what their needs are.","index":605,"end_time":1575.65,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1570.27,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And I think in there is where you can talk about.","index":606,"end_time":1578.21,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1576.05,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And with this, we have this many terminals that we work with and then kind of point to the case studies and logos that Ryan mentioned and I bring up pricing last.","index":607,"end_time":1586.05,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1578.29,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Get them bought in on everything.","index":608,"end_time":1587.41,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1586.05,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, and that''s.","index":609,"end_time":1588.649,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1587.81,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"You''re right.","index":610,"end_time":1589.13,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1588.649,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"So, Colin, real quick, I won''t run you through the whole sales process, but basically we do all that.","index":611,"end_time":1593.09,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1589.13,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"We do an initial call with them where we do that.","index":612,"end_time":1595.09,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1593.09,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Who are you?","index":613,"end_time":1595.53,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1595.09,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"What are you doing?","index":614,"end_time":1596.13,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1595.53,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"What are you trying to accomplish?","index":615,"end_time":1597.25,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1596.21,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Here''s what we know about you.","index":616,"end_time":1598.21,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1597.25,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"We do our deep dive research before we get on a call so that we like, oh, shit, they looked us up.","index":617,"end_time":1602.85,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1598.49,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"They know who we are.","index":618,"end_time":1603.49,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1602.85,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"They know where our locations are.","index":619,"end_time":1604.89,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1603.49,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"They know what we do.","index":620,"end_time":1605.93,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1604.97,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Nothing would fucking piss me off more than enough salesperson get on a call, be like, so tell me a little bit about who you are and what you do.","index":621,"end_time":1611.93,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1606.33,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"You.","index":622,"end_time":1612.41,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1612.01,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"You do that research up front.","index":623,"end_time":1614.17,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1612.41,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"And then we also go through logos.","index":624,"end_time":1616.17,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1614.73,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"We talk about, you know, how we do business different than Ringcentral and everybody else.","index":625,"end_time":1620.01,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1616.17,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"So we do do all that, but.","index":626,"end_time":1622.65,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1620.09,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"And apparently it doesn''t legitimize us in enterprise markets.","index":627,"end_time":1626.73,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1622.81,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Fair enough.","index":628,"end_time":1627.36,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1627,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Which is different.","index":629,"end_time":1628.04,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1627.36,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"But my point being is on this 101, we did do all those things.","index":630,"end_time":1632.6,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1628.04,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"And he''s basically like, so tell me a little bit more about who you are.","index":631,"end_time":1635.96,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1632.6,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"And I''m like, we already told you like eight times.","index":632,"end_time":1639.48,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1636.12,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Do you not.","index":633,"end_time":1640.2,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1639.48,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"You''re not listening.","index":634,"end_time":1641.48,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1640.44,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Yeah, he probably was not listening.","index":635,"end_time":1643.72,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1641.88,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Yeah, he wasn''t listening, right?","index":636,"end_time":1645.24,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1643.72,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Yeah, more than likely.","index":637,"end_time":1647.08,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1645.64,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So is it.","index":638,"end_time":1647.76,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1647.08,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"They''re not paying attention because pricing is in the way.","index":639,"end_time":1650.52,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1647.76,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Right.","index":640,"end_time":1652.32,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1651.96,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"That''s my thing.","index":641,"end_time":1653.08,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1652.32,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"So maybe we should flip the script anyways.","index":642,"end_time":1657.52,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1655,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"That was my thought anyway.","index":643,"end_time":1658.68,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1657.52,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"That''s all I got.","index":644,"end_time":1659.4,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1658.68,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"There''s not enough data to make a change.","index":645,"end_time":1661.32,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1659.72,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"But out of all that, our point is, is I think we need to build an SMB page.","index":646,"end_time":1665.32,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1661.88,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Yep.","index":647,"end_time":1666.12,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1665.56,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And a campaign for it.","index":648,"end_time":1668.76,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1667.48,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I think we drive all our campaigns to this new page.","index":649,"end_time":1672.92,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1670.68,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"I don''t want to say like, maybe not.","index":650,"end_time":1675.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1673.8,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Maybe not like the Microsoft Team 1, but our 1599 page, should you go to that?","index":651,"end_time":1679.25,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1675.28,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"All the sugar to it?","index":652,"end_time":1680.76,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1679.4,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"I mean, perfect icp.","index":653,"end_time":1682.84,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1681.48,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":654,"end_time":1684.36,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1684.04,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"I mean, maybe, maybe it''s a couple of them that, you know, a couple of them that flavor a little bit more towards each campaign.","index":655,"end_time":1690.04,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1684.36,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"But I think we build new landing pages for our campaigns.","index":656,"end_time":1693,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1690.28,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":657,"end_time":1693.56,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1693.08,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"So, Colin, you want to take that one?","index":658,"end_time":1695.479,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1693.96,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Yeah, sure thing.","index":659,"end_time":1696.76,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1695.64,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Lindsay.","index":660,"end_time":1700.6,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1700.12,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Was that everything we had to talk about on that?","index":661,"end_time":1702.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1700.6,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"I believe that it was, yes.","index":662,"end_time":1704.2,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1702.68,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Anything else?","index":663,"end_time":1712.77,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1712.05,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"I did not have anything else.","index":664,"end_time":1715.97,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1714.61,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Lindsay''s pulling her trello board up.","index":665,"end_time":1721.29,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1719.41,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I''m looking at my notes here.","index":666,"end_time":1722.77,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1721.29,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Sounds like you''re feeling better, Lindsay.","index":667,"end_time":1727.17,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1725.73,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I am feeling better, thank you.","index":668,"end_time":1728.85,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1727.33,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"We have registered logos to swap out on the website.","index":669,"end_time":1733.97,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1730.21,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Is that something that you guys want me to do or is that a send it over you guys can do.","index":670,"end_time":1738.79,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1734.05,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Okay.","index":671,"end_time":1739.39,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1738.79,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":672,"end_time":1741.95,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1741.63,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"We got our trademark, Colin.","index":673,"end_time":1743.27,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1741.95,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"After 20 minutes, I finally decided to do it.","index":674,"end_time":1745.79,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1743.27,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Nice.","index":675,"end_time":1746.43,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1745.95,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I had a client that switched between a trademark and a copyright and a registered.","index":676,"end_time":1752.47,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1748.19,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Like every other year.","index":677,"end_time":1753.55,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1752.47,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"It just kept swapping.","index":678,"end_time":1755.79,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1754.59,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"If you don''t, if you don''t renew your registration, then now you have to go back to the tm.","index":679,"end_time":1760.67,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1755.95,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"And then if you don''t get it.","index":680,"end_time":1761.95,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1760.75,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":681,"end_time":1762.35,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1762.03,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"And if you''re not applied, you can''t use the cm.","index":682,"end_time":1764.27,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1762.35,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"You just have to use the copyright.","index":683,"end_time":1765.87,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1764.27,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Right.","index":684,"end_time":1766.45,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1766.25,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"I just can''t imagine why.","index":685,"end_time":1767.85,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1766.45,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"I mean, they just forgot to renew.","index":686,"end_time":1769.25,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1767.85,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Why?","index":687,"end_time":1769.53,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1769.25,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Like you shit, you go through all that work.","index":688,"end_time":1771.13,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1769.53,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":689,"end_time":1771.69,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1771.37,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I have no idea.","index":690,"end_time":1772.33,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1771.69,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And then because they also had different products that they would do trademarks or registered or copyrights on and those would rotate all the time.","index":691,"end_time":1778.73,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1772.33,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":692,"end_time":1779.77,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1779.45,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"I mean, we went.","index":693,"end_time":1780.57,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1779.77,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Knowing how dysfunctional our government is right now, we went in broad on our.","index":694,"end_time":1785.37,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1780.81,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"On our copy, on our trademark for basically anything technology wide.","index":695,"end_time":1789.45,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1785.37,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"He''s like, man, you''re going in way too broad.","index":696,"end_time":1792.09,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1790.09,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"You''re going to get knocked down and I''m like, well, let''s fucking just go broad and see what happened.","index":697,"end_time":1795.69,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1792.09,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Dude, we went through.","index":698,"end_time":1796.41,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1795.69,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"So nothing, nothing technology wise can take that.","index":699,"end_time":1800.81,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1796.57,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"There you go.","index":700,"end_time":1802.05,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1801.53,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Not just UCAs, like AI, anything.","index":701,"end_time":1804.77,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1802.05,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Can''t use technology.","index":702,"end_time":1805.45,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1804.77,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"I don''t know that it matters, but.","index":703,"end_time":1807.05,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1805.77,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"You know, you always run go for ice.","index":704,"end_time":1810.17,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1807.13,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Without the vertical.","index":705,"end_time":1813.73,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1812.81,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"We''re going for now.","index":706,"end_time":1814.65,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1813.73,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"I, I couldn''t do it.","index":707,"end_time":1818.29,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1816.57,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"I am not.","index":708,"end_time":1819.01,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1818.29,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"I''m not that guy.","index":709,"end_time":1820.09,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1819.01,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"That stuff''s crazy.","index":710,"end_time":1823.45,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1822.41,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I think that''s all I had.","index":711,"end_time":1827.25,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1826.29,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":712,"end_time":1828.61,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1828.29,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"So Lindsay, if you can send over those logos and what you want them to swap for, we can take care of that.","index":713,"end_time":1832.69,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1828.61,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And then, yeah, we''ll start putting together the SMB page.","index":714,"end_time":1836.29,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1832.69,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":715,"end_time":1837.25,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1836.69,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"And we''ll get this Microsoft ads campaign live.","index":716,"end_time":1839.33,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1837.25,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Anything else you guys were looking to chat through?","index":717,"end_time":1847.57,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1845.89,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"No.","index":718,"end_time":1848.53,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1848.13,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Yeah, let''s really make sure.","index":719,"end_time":1850.46,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1849.58,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Until I further notice, we''re focusing on that under 100 market.","index":720,"end_time":1853.66,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1850.46,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"That''s really where we want to go.","index":721,"end_time":1854.86,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1853.66,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"So if we need to go back through our Google Ads, we need to go back to our keywords.","index":722,"end_time":1858.06,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1854.94,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Let''s really go back through that and hammer that out, knowing that''s where we are winning.","index":723,"end_time":1862.38,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1858.14,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Yep.","index":724,"end_time":1862.98,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1862.54,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, we''re running audit on our side.","index":725,"end_time":1864.54,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1862.98,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Very good.","index":726,"end_time":1866.06,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1865.42,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":727,"end_time":1868.38,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1867.82,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"You know, I''m going to do that.","index":728,"end_time":1869.38,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1868.38,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"And I got like four deals right now, over 100 stations that we are all out being proposed and those numbers are going to.","index":729,"end_time":1875.22,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1869.38,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"We''ll win all four.","index":730,"end_time":1876.18,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1875.22,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Which.","index":731,"end_time":1876.54,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1876.18,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Man, that would really boost up our numbers.","index":732,"end_time":1879.58,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1877.5,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"I know that would really fuck up our numbers, but.","index":733,"end_time":1881.82,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1879.66,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Well, who''s to say you can''t have both sides, right?","index":734,"end_time":1886.3,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1884.3,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"You can''t.","index":735,"end_time":1886.98,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1886.3,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"You can''t ignore two years worth of data.","index":736,"end_time":1888.78,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1886.98,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":737,"end_time":1890.14,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1889.66,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Well, with.","index":738,"end_time":1892.06,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1890.3,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"With some cleanup.","index":739,"end_time":1893.14,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1892.06,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Right.","index":740,"end_time":1893.34,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1893.14,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"I don''t know about Danielle saying that she''s going to sell to the company she worked for, but it was not mislabeled.","index":741,"end_time":1899.7,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1893.34,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, it was not for the company she works for.","index":742,"end_time":1901.82,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1899.7,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"I believe that the one that you''re referring to was being pitched to a company called AF Group.","index":743,"end_time":1906.54,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1901.82,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"As group.","index":744,"end_time":1909.34,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1908.54,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":745,"end_time":1910.14,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1909.66,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Yep.","index":746,"end_time":1910.9,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1910.46,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"And they said no as no af.","index":747,"end_time":1914.3,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1910.9,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Before I lose you, because I got this.","index":748,"end_time":1919.14,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1917.66,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"I got this on a new spreadsheet.","index":749,"end_time":1920.54,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1919.14,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"It''s AF Group.","index":750,"end_time":1922.78,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1921.66,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"I think so.","index":751,"end_time":1923.74,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1923.1,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":752,"end_time":1924.1,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1923.74,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"I think that''s the one you''re referring to.","index":753,"end_time":1925.34,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1924.1,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"It''s the only one.","index":754,"end_time":1926.14,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1925.34,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":755,"end_time":1929.14,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1928.78,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"During that time frame with that amount.","index":756,"end_time":1930.62,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1929.14,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Of stations and nothing on it, nothing about.","index":757,"end_time":1933.42,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1930.62,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Did she email them?","index":758,"end_time":1934.34,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1933.42,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Was there anything there ever.","index":759,"end_time":1935.62,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1934.34,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"A note here called Lynn.","index":760,"end_time":1939.46,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1937.62,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"She had no recollection of speaking to us.","index":761,"end_time":1942.02,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1939.46,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"So contact associated with the.","index":762,"end_time":1947.62,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1944.42,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Was this the.","index":763,"end_time":1948.5,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1947.62,"speak