ed a deal, honestly.","index":790,"end_time":2030.49,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2027.17,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Okay, fair enough.","index":791,"end_time":2031.409,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2030.49,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Sounds good.","index":792,"end_time":2032.21,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2031.57,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"That helps us a little bit.","index":793,"end_time":2035.37,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2034.21,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"But still.","index":794,"end_time":2035.89,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2035.37,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":795,"end_time":2039.41,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2036.53,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":796,"end_time":2041.42,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2041.18,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"In the early days of HubSpot, it was a little crazy with the data that was being entered.","index":797,"end_time":2047.02,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2041.42,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"This is the most, like.","index":798,"end_time":2055.1,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2053.98,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Doesn''t tell me anything website.","index":799,"end_time":2056.62,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2055.1,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"For AF Group.","index":800,"end_time":2059.5,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2058.46,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":801,"end_time":2060.3,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2059.82,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Money laundering.","index":802,"end_time":2062.86,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2061.98,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"It''s just a holding company for insurance brands.","index":803,"end_time":2066.86,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2063.18,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"You know, Ryan, I know you don''t get up this way very often, but you know what used to be the Max and Irma''s right there at the mall?","index":8