108.76,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2106.68,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"So I''m not speculating.","index":819,"end_time":2110.24,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2108.76,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Like, you know, that''s just.","index":820,"end_time":2112.36,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2110.24,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"That''s just how it goes.","index":821,"end_time":2113.52,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2112.36,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"There''s.","index":822,"end_time":2114.56,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2114,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"There''s a Coney island on Van dyke and like 18 mile.","index":823,"end_time":2118.04,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2115.28,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"It''s been there forever, but yeah, don''t go in there.","index":824,"end_time":2120,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2118.04,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"They''re not interested.","index":825,"end_time":2121.23,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2120.47,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"They don''t Serve food.","index":826,"end_time":2122.15,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2121.23,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"I saw there was a Reddit post of a kid.","index":827,"end_time":2125.31,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2123.11,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"He''s like, I was pretty sure the mafia ran this place.","index":828,"end_time":2127.67,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2125.31,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"It was like, in New York or Chicago or something like that.","index":829,"end_time":2129.83,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2127.67,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"So he''s like, I went in there, sat down, and the guys looked at me like I was crazy.","index":830,"end_time":2135.03,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2130.63,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"And he said, so I ordered a pizza.","index":831,"end_time":2136.95,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2135.03,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"And they''re like, all right.","index":832,"end_time":2139.87,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2137.43,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"He said it took him, like, it took like an hour and a half for them.","index":833,"end_time":2142.95,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2139.87,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"And then they came back, and they came back with a pizza and they said, it''s free on us, kid.","index":834,"end_time":2149.72,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2143.67,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Get out of here.","index":835,"end_time":2150.36,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2149.72,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"They just order it from somewhere else.","index":836,"end_time":2155,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2153.32,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, exactly.","index":837,"end_time":2157.08,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2155.4,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"How far is it from Lansing?","index":838,"end_time":2160.44,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2158.36,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Lansing''s an hour, because that''s where that 4af group is.","index":839,"end_time":2165.08,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2161.24,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"All right, I''m going to clean this up a little bit, see if this makes it any better or worse.","index":840,"end_time":2170.44,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2167.08,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Yeah, anything that''s in, like, early 2024, take a hard look at, because.","index":841,"end_time":2176.35,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2171.96,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Well, I''m just going to ask.","index":842,"end_time":2177.83,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2176.91,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"I''m going to.","index":843,"end_time":2178.19,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2177.83,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"As soon as I get off this.","index":844,"end_time":2178.87,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2178.19,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fis