  '[{"text":"Implement updates to the price hover page and tech mode go page as per Lindsay’s feedback (05:13)","completed":false},{"text":"Launch Microsoft ads campaign with current assets and budget, pending next week’s budget review (06:39)","completed":false},{"text":"Begin development of SMB-focused landing page to target Google Ads traffic effectively (28:41)","completed":false},{"text":"Conduct audit of Google Ads keywords and campaigns to realign toward under-100 seat market segment (31:02)","completed":false},{"text":"Take responsibility for swapping registered trademarked logos on website once Lindsay sends the updated files (30:37)","completed":false},{"text":"Perform sales data cleanup in HubSpot for mislabeled deals and coordinate with sales team to confirm qualification of leads (36:07)","completed":false},{"text":"Continue reviewing website pages to ensure consistent UCaaS branding and company references (13:42)","completed":false},{"text":"Provide copy and updated registered trademark logos for website update (30:37)","completed":false},{"text":"Investigate and correct deal record inaccuracies in CRM, especially relating to unpitched or lost deals (30:37)","completed":false},{"text":"Continue reviewing two-year sales data to verify win rates and deal qualification accuracy, specifically cleaning up dubious over-100 seat losses (14:04)","completed":false},{"text":"Share insights and data with team to inform SMB landing page and campaign strategy (14:04)","completed":false},{"text":"Coordinate with sales team (Mike and Kurt) post-call to get details on unclear deals and update CRM data accordingly (36:18)","completed":false},{"text":"Contribute perspective on developing case studies and logos to reinforce trust messaging during sales process (22:40)","completed":false},{"text":"Monitor effectiveness of AI-generated blog content improvements focusing on executive summaries to improve SEO and AI relevance (07:31)","completed":false}]'::jsonb,
