ure if that''s something that we can get access to.","index":198,"end_time":1010.17,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1002.89,"speaker_name":"gabrielbencosme"},{"text":"So we can test around.","index":199,"end_time":1012.05,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1010.41,"speaker_name":"gabrielbencosme"},{"text":"But you should have a core seat.","index":200,"end_time":1015.53,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1012.05,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"If I switch it to a developer seat, I wonder if that''ll change your access.","index":201,"end_time":1019.05,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1016.01,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay.","index":202,"end_time":1020.89,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1020.33,"speaker_name":"gabrielbencosme"},{"text":"Because I know we switched it to the digital GPS at Ponce bank.","index":203,"end_time":1024.81,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1021.45,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So I guess as we go in this, in this timeline, if there''s any additional things that come up, you know, we can maybe add them in live in.","index":204,"end_time":1037.899,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1028.299,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"In either the notes or what have you.","index":205,"end_time":1040.259,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1037.899,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"So we could just track that and make sure that we have that.","index":206,"end_time":1045.259,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1040.259,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"And then if we need to move that due date, you know, we can, we can do that.","index":207,"end_time":1049.659,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1045.499,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"The, the line 13 defining mass.","index":208,"end_time":1054.16,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1050.299,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Is that the, the task that we''re speaking about right now or did we not start that?","index":209,"end_time":1060.36,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1054.16,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Was that something else?","index":210,"end_time":1061.76,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1060.76,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"The.","index":211,"end_time":1062.12,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1061.76,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"What you guys were just talking about?","index":212,"end_time":1065.64,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1064.28,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"So what Gabe was just referring to was just the API connection itself and understanding how HubSpot connects.","index":213,"end_time":1072.6,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1067.159,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Those.","index":214,"end_time":1072.84,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1072.6,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"The masking rules would be more towards the custom fields list that we have and just determining what of that needs to be masked.","index":215,"end_time":1080.85,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1073.4,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay, so the, the.","index":216,"end_time":1082.61,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1081.17,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"That, that point.","index":217,"end_time":1084.29,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1082.69,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"So where was that on the actual timeline?","index":218,"end_time":1087.17,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1084.53,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Just so I can kind of follow in.","index":219,"end_time":1089.09,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1087.49,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"In sequence that task.","index":220,"end_time":1091.01,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1089.09,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Is that the one you look you''re pointing to configure API authentication.","index":221,"end_time":1094.69,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1091.17,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":222,"end_time":1096.81,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1096.29,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So again, sorry, this is the, we''re in the midst of upgrading the, this spreadsheet to be more broken out.","index":223,"end_time":1102.89,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1096.81,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So that was with data models and custom fields and HubSpot environments on the original timeline.","index":224,"end_time":1111.2,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1102.89,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay.","index":225,"end_time":1112.32,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1111.84,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"So if what we can do is we can just make sure that like the tasks are happening in sequence and if they have to happen at the same time, that''s fine.","index":226,"end_time":1119.68,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1112.32,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"So the API that decision, what is the due date for that?","index":227,"end_time":1124.56,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1119.92,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Because I want to give Ashley and Gabe like a North Star to work towards so we can make sure that the next meeting, you know, we have everything that needs to happen.","index":228,"end_time":1132.83,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1124.56,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Yeah, so.","index":229,"end_time":1134.03,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1133.23,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So the thing that we would like this week is if possible, just a sign off on the custom fields that are going to communicate between all the systems.","index":230,"end_time":1141.71,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1134.11,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"That way we can build it inside of HubSpot properties.","index":231,"end_time":1144.27,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1141.71,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"After that then we would load in the test contacts that were shared with us and from there then we would enable the API sync between the systems once we confirm that everything''s communicating correctly.","index":232,"end_time":1158.01,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1145.15,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay, so can you point to those tasks on the, the timeline and then we''ll make sure that we''re aligned on the due dates and you know, the team can ask if they have any questions.","index":233,"end_time":1170.28,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1158.48,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"The one thing that I''m thinking is, is that on the last call we, we talked about like breaking out the, that overall list of fields into priorities.","index":234,"end_time":1178.6,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1170.28,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"But then based off of just conversations back and forth with Ashley offline, I''m not, I, I think that she was asking to break the map because maybe of a different thought.","index":235,"end_time":1187.17,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1178.6,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"So I don''t know if we still need that to move forward.","index":236,"end_time":1189.53,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1187.17,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"So Ashley, you know, feel free to jump in there.","index":237,"end_time":1191.65,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1189.53,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Yeah, I don''t think that we need that.","index":238,"end_time":1194.73,"speaker_id":6,"start_time":1192.61,"speaker_name":"Ashlie Taska"},{"text":"It was more.","index":239,"end_time":1195.49,"speaker_id":6,"start_time":1194.73,"speaker_name":"Ashlie Taska"},{"text":"So the other understanding that we had of the project having all the fields there, that''s, that''s fine.","index":240,"end_time":1204.81,"speaker_id":6,"start_time":1195.49,"speaker_name":"Ashlie Taska"},{"text":"It was just building out workflows in mulesoft that we were more concerned about having to do by end of month.","index":241,"end_time":1211.57,"speaker_id":6,"start_time":1204.81,"speaker_name":"Ashlie Taska"},{"text":"So.","index":242,"end_time":1211.97,"speaker_id":6,"start_time":1211.57,"speaker_name":"Ashlie Taska"},{"text":"Got it.","index":243,"end_time":1212.64,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1212.24,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Okay.","index":244,"end_time":1213.4,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1212.88,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"So, so that, that spreadsheet, which is the list of fields, obviously we''re going to be doing mapping towards where is that on the task?","index":245,"end_time":1221.68,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1213.4,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Like what line item is that was Then correct me if I''m wrong and we can, we can kind of say that that list is quote unquote approved, right?","index":246,"end_time":1229.56,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1222.4,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"There was no concerns with anything on that list, right?","index":247,"end_time":1231.76,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1229.56,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Yeah, I mean that''s what we went through and shared with last week.","index":248,"end_time":1238.6,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1235.44,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So, yeah, if there''s, if there hasn''t been any feedback or any Changes there then.","index":249,"end_time":1241.36,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1238.6,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay.","index":250,"end_time":1242.61,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1242.13,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"And Gabe, from your side, do you need anything to start?","index":251,"end_time":1248.45,"speaker_id":6,"start_time":1243.73,"speaker_name":"Ashlie Taska"},{"text":"Well where.","index":252,"end_time":1249.17,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1248.61,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Yeah to casino.","index":253,"end_time":1250.77,"speaker_id":6,"start_time":1249.17,"speaker_name":"Ashlie Taska"},{"text":"Where''s the.","index":254,"end_time":1251.41,"speaker_id":6,"start_time":1250.85,"speaker_name":"Ashlie Taska"},{"text":"What''s the due date for.